text.tspan: Each pin is 3.3V tolerant and can source/sink
Each cluster of I/O pins can source 46mA and
sink 65mA. Clusters are defined as Yellow, Pink,
Green, Blue, Red, and Orange outlines.

g.text: Only Ports with * can be configured to do I2C

text.tspan: Pin can only be A,B,C,D,E,F,G or H at any time
